### 400 Bad Request - Create agent with empty fields
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "role": "",
  "description": ""
}


### 400 Bad Request - Create agent with spaces only
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "   ",
  "role": "   ",
  "description": "   "
}


### 400 Bad Request - Update agent with invalid fields
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/agents/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "role": "",
  "description": ""
}

### 201 Created - Create valid agent
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Validation Test Agent",
  "role": "Tester",
  "description": "This should be saved successfully"
}

### Direct backend
GET http://localhost:8081/api/agents

### Through gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/api/agents